    "title": "Scid vs. PC",
    "pageid": 5966,
    "redirects": [],
    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/User_Interface\" title=\"User Interface\">User Interface</a> * <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a> * Scid vs. PC</b><br />\n<b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Software\" title=\"Software\">Software</a> * <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">Databases</a> * Scid vs. PC</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:130px;\"><a href=\"http://scidvspc.sourceforge.net/images/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/b/b0/Scidvspclogo.jpg\" width=\"128\" height=\"128\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Scidvspclogo.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Scid vs. PC Logo  <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><br />\n<b>Scid vs. PC</b>,<br />\nan open source Chess GUI with the ability to run detailed chess analysis, to create and query huge <a href=\"/Databases\" title=\"Databases\">databases</a>, to play on-line with <a href=\"/index.php?title=FICS&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"FICS (page does not exist)\">FICS</a> and against computer opponents, and to <a href=\"/Tournament_Manager\" title=\"Tournament Manager\">manage computer tournaments</a>. \nIt is a fork of <a href=\"/Shane_Hudson\" title=\"Shane Hudson\">Shane Hudson's</a> Chess Information Database (<a href=\"/SCID\" title=\"SCID\">SCID</a>), started in 2009 by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, and requires installation of <a href=\"/index.php?title=Tcl-Tk&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Tcl-Tk (page does not exist)\">Tcl/Tk</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. Scid vs. PC runs under <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a>, <a href=\"/Mac_OS\" title=\"Mac OS\">Mac OS</a> and <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a> computers, supporting <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> and <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant engines. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Screenshot\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Screenshot</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scid_vs._PC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Chess_Assistant\" title=\"Chess Assistant\">Chess Assistant</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/ChessBase_(Database)\" title=\"ChessBase (Database)\">ChessBase (Database)</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessDB&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ChessDB (page does not exist)\">ChessDB</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chess_Query_Language\" title=\"Chess Query Language\">Chess Query Language</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/ChessX\" title=\"ChessX\">ChessX</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Tournament_Manager\" title=\"Tournament Manager\">Tournament Manager</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/SCID\" title=\"SCID\">SCID</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Scid_on_the_Go&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Scid on the Go (page does not exist)\">Scid on the Go</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Screenshot\">Screenshot</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scid_vs._PC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Screenshot\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"http://scidvspc.sourceforge.net/images/scidvspc.png\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Scidvspc.jpg\" src=\"/images/6/6c/Scidvspc.jpg\" width=\"1200\" height=\"511\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div>\n<p>Scid vs. PC Screenshot \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scid_vs._PC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scid_vs._PC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36388\">Scid fork and Phalanx news</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 17, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Phalanx\" title=\"Phalanx\">Phalanx</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=38213\">Scid vs. PC 4.3</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 26, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39982\">Scid vs. PC 4.5</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 07, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41136\">Scid vs. PC 4.6</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 19, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42453\">Scid vs. PC 4.7</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42777\">ScidVsPC/Mac</a> by <a href=\"/Julien_Marcel\" title=\"Julien Marcel\">Julien Marcel</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 06, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44754\">Scid vs. PC 4.8</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 10, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47810\">Scid vs. PC 4.9</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 19, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=50272\">Scid vs. PC 4.11</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 29, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=563584\">Scid vs. PC 4.12</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 26, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=54153\">Scid vs. PC 4.13</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 26, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scid_vs._PC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55910\">Scid vs. PC 4.14</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 05, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=58322\">Scid vs. PC 4.15</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 22, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=59027\">Scid vs. PC 4.16</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 24, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61165\">Scid / Scid vs. PC - ChessBase (.ctg) and Arena (.abk)</a> by <a href=\"/Norbert_Raimund_Leisner\" title=\"Norbert Raimund Leisner\">Norbert Raimund Leisner</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/CTG\" title=\"CTG\">CTG</a>, <a href=\"/ABK\" title=\"ABK\">ABK</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=65815\">Scid vs PC with CQL , build issue</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 25, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess_Query_Language\" title=\"Chess Query Language\">CQL</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=66562\">Scid vs PC CQL 5.2 feature</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 11, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71135\">Scid vs. PC - EPD Export feature</a> by <a href=\"/Steven_Atkinson\" title=\"Steven Atkinson\">Steven Atkinson</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 29, 2019&#160;» <a href=\"/Extended_Position_Description\" title=\"Extended Position Description\">Extended Position Description</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scid_vs._PC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sourceforge.net/projects/scidvspc/\">Project Page</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://sourceforge.net/blog/after-scid-row-a-new-chess-app-is-born/\">After Scid row, a new chess app is born | SourceForge Community Blog</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://scidvspc.sourceforge.net/\">Scid vs. PC</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://scidvspc.sourceforge.net/doc/Formats.htm\">Scid File Formats</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Scid_vs._PC&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Images from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://scidvspc.sourceforge.net/images/\">Scid vs. PC - Index of /images</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.activestate.com/products/activetcl/downloads/\">Tcl/Tk</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">Up one Level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301074834\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.017 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.019 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 59/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 114/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000  